    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37320</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_032_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>剣士に魔法使いに……
なんでもなれるんだな、オレら</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We can become swordsmen, mages... We can become anything, huh?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <StructId>1</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38096</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_032_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そりゃ『なりきり士』だし
服があれば、なんにでもなれるけど……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, we are "Mimickers." As long as we have the outfits, we can become anything...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <StructId>2</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38452</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_032_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>別に服なんてなくてもなれるんだよ。
バジルさん言ってた、オレら真っ白なんだって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We don't even need outfits to become something. Basil said we're completely blank slates.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <StructId>3</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39208</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_032_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だったら『なりきり士』の力に
頼らない方がいいんじゃない？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Then maybe we shouldn't rely on the power of "Mimickers"?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <StructId>4</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39564</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_032_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そっだらことは、ダメだ、&lt;MEL&gt;&lt;MEL&gt;！
なーんかあって、ケガでもしたら大事だど！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That won't do, Mel! If something happens and you get hurt, it'll be a big deal!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <StructId>5</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>25</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41160</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_032_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>大体、服ないとダメって、
便利なようで、めんどくさいぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Honestly, needing outfits is convenient, but it's also a hassle.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <StructId>6</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41660</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_032_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>着替えなきゃだし、
このヘンテコタンス野郎もいつも一緒だしさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We have to change clothes, and that weird wardrobe guy is always with us.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <StructId>7</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42304</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_032_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おめぇの、そのマヌケヅラは、魔物に殴られた方が
ちっとはマシになるかもしんねーな。へへへ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Maybe if a monster punched that dumb face of yours, it might improve a little. Heh heh.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <StructId>8</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>25</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43708</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_032_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>てめぇは……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You little...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <StructId>9</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
